{"tid":1874454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲㷫政府 阿澤兩萬口罩贈醫護","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T08:55:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19697226a625bdd64f9f8c340639beda6ebcfd86","tid":1874454,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200211/TRBDWWQLH2OO7VWTS5FRDS2AN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200211%2FTRBDWWQLH2OO7VWTS5FRDS2AN4%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=5aad8d29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200211%2FTRBDWWQLH2OO7VWTS5FRDS2AN4%2F&h=8028cb2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200211/TRBDWWQLH2OO7VWTS5FRDS2AN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n有啲㷫政府 阿澤兩萬口罩贈醫護<br />\n<br />\n向來為社會發聲的杜汶澤，眼見武漢肺炎肆虐，林鄭領導的香港特區政府至今仍拒絕全面封關，加上未能有效採購口罩，令市民失去信心。早前阿澤在外地訂購了兩萬個口罩，昨日傍晚已送到香港，他打算送給前線醫護及其家屬。而近日所見，香港市民瘋狂搶購食米和廁紙，口罩更加是一罩難求，甚至被炒至天價。一班在防疫最前線的醫護人員，更未能分到足夠口罩及防護用具，反而政府懲教署生產、印有「CSI」的口罩近日卻屢次被爆於網上明目張膽地出售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581343000_f510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581343000_f510.jpg&h=a4caf28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤向來關注社會，將早前在外地訂購的口罩轉贈給香港醫護人員。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581342999_f2c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581342999_f2c6.jpg&h=2d04fad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤昨日在社交網留言，指自己能力有限，只是希望盡一點綿力，並教人健身抗疫。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581342999_8ea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581342999_8ea9.jpg&h=abd2abef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠及家屬<br />\n<br />\n阿澤昨日接受《蘋果》訪問時透露，不單會將口罩轉贈一班前線醫護，就連他們的家屬都會受惠，他說︰「見到班醫護咁慘，香港市民都好痛心。唔明林鄭點樣去搵口罩嗰個資源，人人都係咁搵，大家都係咁撲，佢就搵唔到。開頭我搵咗幾萬個，但都係送唔到嚟香港，直至到今日嚟咗一批，打算送兩萬隻畀醫護同佢哋家屬，知道係好少，但我能力只係咁樣，無論財力或者搵到口罩方法。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581342998_3433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581342998_3433.jpg&h=ced76d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤表示兩萬個口罩昨日已運抵他的公司。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人人自救<br />\n<br />\n對於這個決定，阿澤透露是源於有位老友的醫護太太一番說話，他說︰「聽老友位醫護老婆講，政府醫院居然叫醫護自己買口罩、面罩返工，我聽到覺得『有冇搞錯呀！』你唔叫差佬自己買槍返工。咁呢啲係保護自己人身安全措施，有啲㷫所以諗辦法買啲口罩返嚟。𠵱家梗係人人自救啦，呢個政府唔X推翻佢已經好畀面啦。大有大搞，細有細救，我哋又唔係劉鑾雄、李嘉誠咁樣，有幾多錢幾多辦法，能力範圍之內做到幾多得幾多，只要人人都係咁做，相信香港係有得救。」其後，阿澤在個人的fb中轉載有關報道，並留言：「好抱歉，呢期窄窄地！身家有限，亦買咗好多次都失敗！兩萬頂住先！」<br />\n<br />\n採訪︰何永寧"},{"pid":"6b36edd3bde896d33db322338ff13e615501d096","tid":1874454,"uid":208239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd17cf9b3dd18b4d5da4f9175e1e19114de235e","tid":1874454,"uid":35914,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"希望佢醒目係交比工會d人啦"},{"pid":"7e42fecddc276bd39085e3da1a3e2e13b64de697","tid":1874454,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"藍絲蝗護:又有傻仔送上門"},{"pid":"25f4ca31f8a979fa15e6a74690dde10288aeb62d","tid":1874454,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a3711103be51abc7b2ee425b7cfbc89df8f252","tid":1874454,"uid":11447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"真接比前線醫護 唔好比啲畜牲有機可乘"},{"pid":"d48ab04930151cd40ca9a490b11e564501333e59","tid":1874454,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a3711103be51abc7b2ee425b7cfbc89df8f252","tid":1874454,"uid":11447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"真接比前線醫護 唔好比啲畜牲有機可乘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">直</span>"},{"pid":"2cf7b48de07bf7a2bc0f6e710da20a5af9aa276b","tid":1874454,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"課金去lateshow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada928266b56d744d247e60a4fc6bc9304d84f3c","tid":1874454,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"政府真係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5aca89ddab9b037f3b54838c57a356b1bad4f8e","tid":1874454,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"ha唔做<br />\n總會有人做埋ha嗰份<br />\nha又嬴"},{"pid":"3671564208842c2e929ad833d0a41c2924f5fbd7","tid":1874454,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698edcb67cecb97ea9c80158dd793e4694cc0c95","tid":1874454,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"咪再比d成日鬧後生仔既藍畜廢老"}]}